snippet.textDisplay:
I’m pretty impressed w skincare but some tips
- don’t use the face powder twice a day! u only need to use a couple times a week
- don’t double exfoliate , you’ll compromise your skin barrier! u can alternate it w the tatcha rice powder
- u don’t have to slap ur face, i gently pat in the product so that it is evenly spread! u can gently do a lymphatic massage on ur face w ur hands or a gua sha tool if that’s ur thing :)
snippet.textOriginal:
I’m pretty impressed w skincare but some tips
- don’t use the face powder twice a day! u only need to use a couple times a week
- don’t double exfoliate , you’ll compromise your skin barrier! u can alternate it w the tatcha rice powder
- u don’t have to slap ur face, i gently pat in the product so that it is evenly spread! u can gently do a lymphatic massage on ur face w ur hands or a gua sha tool if that’s ur thing :)
